==Popular culture== The Buddy Greco recording was the first piece of music heard in the first episode of the 2012 television series ''[[Pan Am (TV series)|Pan Am]]''.
The song is used multiple times in various forms throughout the 2015 Japanese animated film ''[[The Anthem of the Heart]]''.
